<section_header_level_1><loc_54><loc_166><loc_197><loc_174>IX. TRANSITORY PROVISION</section_header_level_1>
<text><loc_53><loc_181><loc_438><loc_236>All PAPs already under procurement and/or payment processes initiated pursuant to previous guidelines and ongoing at the time of effectivity of this Order shall be allowed to continue until its completion, subject to applicable government accounting and auditing rules and regulations. ROs and SDOs are hereby directed to ensure the settlement of payments for obligations arising from duly conducted activities and valid contracts. activity commenced thereafter shall be governed by the provisions of this Order. Any</text>
